<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:402px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Spiceopus_screenshot.png" class="image" title="Screen shot of Spice OPUS, a fork of Berkeley SPICE"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/7/76/Spiceopus_screenshot.png/400px-Spiceopus_screenshot.png" width="400" height="210" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
